#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.topk"
msgstr "# triton.language.topk"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:4
msgid "简介：返回输入张量 `x` 沿指定维度的前 `k` 个最大元素，返回结果按从大到小排序。"
msgstr "Introduction: Returns the top `k` largest elements of the input tensor `x` along the specified dimension, with the results sorted in descending order."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.topk(x, k, dim: constexpr | None = None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| `x` | `tensor` | 输入张量 |\n"
"| `k` | `int` | 要返回的top元素数量，必须是 2 的幂 |\n"
"| `dim` | `constexpr int` 或 `None` | 要查找 top k 元素的维度；该参数需要在编译期确定；如果为 `None`，则使用最后一个维度；当前仅支持最后一个维度 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| `x` | `tensor` | Input tensor |\n"
"| `k` | `int` | Number of top elements to return, must be a power of 2 |\n"
"| `dim` | `constexpr int` or `None` | Dimension along which to find the top k elements; this parameter must be determined at compile time; if `None`, the last dimension is used; currently only the last dimension is supported |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`out`：输出张量的 shape 与输入张量一致，但指定维度长度变为 `k`\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`out`: The shape of the output tensor is the same as the input tensor, but the length of the specified dimension becomes `k`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | × | × | √ | √ | × | √ | × |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | × | × | √ | √ | × | √ | × |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:22
msgid ""
"结论：Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 int32、uint8、int64、float64、bool 支持。\n"
"torch_npu 支持 uint8。\n"
msgstr "Conclusion: Compared to GPU, Ascend lacks support for int32, uint8, int64, float64, and bool. torch_npu supports uint8."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:26
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围 |\n"
"| ------ | ------------ |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5 维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 仅支持 1~5 维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ------------------------ |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5 dimensional tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5 dimensional tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5-dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:34
msgid "毕升编译器限制，int32、uint8、int64、float64、bool 无法实现。"
msgstr "Due to limitations of the Bisheng compiler, int32, uint8, int64, float64, and bool cannot be implemented."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:36
msgid ""
"当前 `topk` 仅返回最大值，不支持通过参数切换为返回最小值。\n"
"`dim` 仅支持最后一个维度。\n"
"`k` 必须为 2 的幂。\n"
msgstr ""
"Currently, `topk` only returns the maximum values and does not support switching to return minimum values via parameters.  \n"
"`dim` only supports the last dimension.  \n"
"`k` must be a power of 2.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:38
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:40
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 沿最后一个维度取前 `k` 个最大元素："
msgstr "The following example implements taking the top `k` largest elements from the input tensor `x` along its last dimension:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/topk.md:42
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def topk_kernel_2d(X, Z, M: tl.constexpr, N: tl.constexpr, K: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(0)\n"
"    offs_m = pid\n"
"    offs_n = tl.arange(0, N)\n"
"    offs = offs_m * N + offs_n\n"
"    x = tl.load(X + offs)\n"
"    z = tl.topk(x, K, dim=0)\n"
"    tl.store(Z + offs_m * K + tl.arange(0, K), z)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

